$PAR
\( y($a4) = {}\) \{ans_rule(20)\}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") \}

$PAR
While the approximate solution found above is
\( y($a4) \approx {}\) \{ans_rule(20)\}
\{ AnswerFormatHelp("numbers") \}

